column2: MAYBANK KIM ENG SECURITIES PTE. LTD.

column1: SHAREHOLDING IN THE HANDS OF PUBLIC
BASED  ON  THE  INFORMATION  PROVIDED  TO  THE  COMPANY  AS  AT  21  JUNE  2019,  APPROXIMATELY  76.95%  OF  THE
ISSUED ORDINARY SHARES OF THE COMPANY WERE HELD BY THE PUBLIC. ACCORDINGLY, THE COMPANY HAS COMPLIED
WITH RULE 723 OF THE LISTING MANUAL OF SGX-ST, WHICH REQUIRE THAT AT LEAST 10% OF THE TOTAL NUMBER ISSUED
SHARES  (EXCLUDING  PREFERENCE  SHARES  AND  CONVERTIBLE  EQUITY  SECURITIES  AND  TREASURY  SHARES)  IN  A  CLASS
THAT IS LISTED IS AT ALL TIMES HELD BY THE PUBLIC.
